title: WEDNESDAY 5/5 - JIMMY GAROPPOLO SPEAKS
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 5/5 - JIMMY GAROPPOLO SPEAKS
description:
We hear from Jimmy Garoppolo (0:06) for the first time since the 49ers drafted Trey Lance. Terry Bradshaw (1:18) has some not-so-nice things to say about Aaron Rodgers. Zach Wilson (2:22) talks about turning around the Jets, while Quinnen Williams (2:43) suffers an injury. Plus, Jerome Bettis (3:00) talks about the Steelers drafting of Najee Harris
